Guess what!

01:39.307 --> 01:41.142
"Good Day, USA"

01:41.142 --> 01:42.227
picked Green River

01:42.393 --> 01:44.479
for their Christmas Eve morningremote broadcast.

01:44.479 --> 01:47.023
Our parade is going to be seenacross the entire country!

01:47.065 --> 01:49.234
[squealing with delight]

01:49.275 --> 01:50.485
Oh, my gosh.This is amazing.

01:52.153 --> 01:54.072
Wait. Are youmessing with me?

01:54.114 --> 01:55.490
