02:08.002 --> 02:09.002
My parents have been trying

02:09.002 --> 02:10.505
to get them to come herefor years,

02:10.505 --> 02:12.340
and my grandparents before them.

02:12.340 --> 02:14.008
You're the onethat got it to 50.

02:14.008 --> 02:15.468
This is all you.

02:15.510 --> 02:17.178
