02:57.844 --> 02:59.888
"Find the jolly!"

02:59.929 --> 03:02.599
Ho-ho-ho!

03:03.725 --> 03:05.185
Ho-ho-ho!

03:06.102 --> 03:07.687
See? That's better, huh?

03:09.606 --> 03:11.482
