03:27.165 --> 03:28.333
and I'm in charge of the parade

03:28.374 --> 03:29.542
that keepsthe entire town going.

03:29.584 --> 03:30.668
Well, maybe one year,

03:30.835 --> 03:32.253
you could let someone elsetake over the parade.

03:32.253 --> 03:34.088
I can't do that.

03:34.130 --> 03:36.925
Owning the storemeans organizing the parade.

03:36.925 --> 03:37.592
It always has.

03:37.717 --> 03:38.927
I mean, who wouldn't love

03:39.177 --> 03:40.595
to be surrounded by Christmasevery single day of the year?

03:40.595 --> 03:42.222
Mark, apparently.

03:42.263 --> 03:43.932
He didn't get it.

03:43.932 --> 03:45.516
He never did.

03:53.107 --> 03:54.108
Grace Long?

03:55.818 --> 03:56.778
Yes. That's me.

03:56.778 --> 03:57.612
Leslie Mitchell,

03:57.779 --> 03:58.780
field producerfor "Good Day, USA"

03:58.821 --> 03:59.572
in New York.

03:59.614 --> 04:00.865
We spoke on the phone?

04:01.616 --> 04:02.951
Of course.So nice to meet you.

04:02.951 --> 04:03.993
Nice to meet you.Hello.

04:04.035 --> 04:05.078
Hi.

04:05.119 --> 04:06.246
Welcome to Green River.

04:07.872 --> 04:09.374
I'm just trying to geta lay of the land.

04:09.415 --> 04:11.876
Is it okay if I takea little video of your store?

04:12.710 --> 04:14.754
-Of course. Go right ahead.-Wait! Wait, wait.

04:15.630 --> 04:17.089
-Caroline, knock it off.-Okay, okay.

04:17.130 --> 04:19.759
And five, four, three--

04:19.801 --> 04:22.720
Actually, I'm justusing my phone

04:22.762 --> 04:24.264
so we don't need a countdown.

04:24.305 --> 04:25.598
Gotcha.

04:32.647 --> 04:35.316
[Christmas music playing]

04:36.192 --> 04:37.402
[laughs in delight]

04:37.443 --> 04:38.945
That is adorable.

04:42.156 --> 04:44.409
Ooh, what's back there?

04:44.450 --> 04:46.619
Oh, just this and that.

04:46.661 --> 04:48.997
These are wonderful.Who's the artist?

04:48.997 --> 04:50.290
Actually, that's me.

04:50.331 --> 04:53.042
[Leslie]: You're very talented.

04:53.084 --> 04:54.502
It's just a side hobby.

04:54.502 --> 04:56.337
["Santa"]: Ho-ho-ho!

04:56.379 --> 04:57.755
What's that?

04:57.797 --> 04:59.757
That is"Selfies with Santa."

05:00.758 --> 05:02.844
"Selfies with Santa"?This I gotta see.

05:04.220 --> 05:05.179
[quietly] Yes!

05:05.179 --> 05:06.639
And look at you!

05:06.681 --> 05:10.518
