05:13.021 --> 05:14.397
Oh... Oh!

05:14.439 --> 05:15.481
Oh, so cute.

05:15.523 --> 05:16.399
I know.

05:16.441 --> 05:18.109
-The kids just love him.-Beautiful.

05:18.151 --> 05:19.694
Oh, boy...

05:19.736 --> 05:21.362
you've donethis before.

05:21.362 --> 05:23.698
Oh! Merry Christmas!

05:23.740 --> 05:26.242
He really isthe best Santa.

05:27.577 --> 05:31.039
Thank you so muchand Merry Christmas!

05:31.039 --> 05:32.874
Hi, Mrs. Claus!

05:33.875 --> 05:34.876
Hello!

05:36.210 --> 05:37.295
And hello, Santa.

05:38.713 --> 05:41.007
Well, it's goodto see you, Gracie.

05:41.049 --> 05:44.260
And I bet that you wanta selfie with Santa.

05:44.302 --> 05:45.345
I kinda do.

05:49.307 --> 05:51.059
[Santa]: Oh, here we go.

05:51.059 --> 05:53.186
One, two, three.

05:55.980 --> 05:57.607
How are you doing withall the parade preparations?

05:57.648 --> 05:58.816
You holding up okay?

05:58.858 --> 06:00.401
I'm great.

06:00.443 --> 06:03.279
Everybody knows where to goand what to do.

06:03.321 --> 06:04.322
Practically runs itself.

06:04.363 --> 06:06.115
That's what your momused to say.

06:07.325 --> 06:08.534
I know you missyour folks the most

06:08.576 --> 06:10.161
during the holidays.

06:10.203 --> 06:11.204
