10:02.560 --> 10:04.645
No, he went throughall the training.

10:04.687 --> 10:06.314
He was supposed to take overthe school someday

10:06.314 --> 10:07.273
when I retired,

10:07.481 --> 10:09.692
but let's just sayhe never wanted to follow

10:09.734 --> 10:11.485
in Santa's footsteps.

10:11.485 --> 10:12.862
Getting into a Santa suit

10:12.903 --> 10:15.573
is the last thingthat Ben wants to do.

10:16.657 --> 10:17.616
Yeah, but I'm sure

10:17.658 --> 10:18.618
when he understandswhat's at stake,

10:18.659 --> 10:19.577
he'd be happy to help.

10:19.619 --> 10:21.287
Don't get your hopes up.

10:22.997 --> 10:25.333
[Grace]: Hi, is this Ben?

10:25.333 --> 10:26.083
[Ben]: Yes.

10:26.167 --> 10:27.001
[Grace]: This is Grace Long

10:27.043 --> 10:28.794
I know why you're calling.

10:28.836 --> 10:29.879
So you'll do it then?

10:29.920 --> 10:31.839
You'll stand in for your dad?

10:31.881 --> 10:32.840
The whole town

10:32.882 --> 10:33.924
would be so grateful.

10:33.966 --> 10:35.134
Are you sure my dad can't do it?

10:35.176 --> 10:36.927
