10:40.431 --> 10:41.515
So he's not okay?

10:41.515 --> 10:42.725
No, he will be,

10:42.767 --> 10:44.602
but you know, with his cast the way it is,

10:44.644 --> 10:45.728
and his arm in a sling,

10:45.770 --> 10:46.729
he just can't be Santa.

10:46.771 --> 10:49.190
And according to him...

10:49.231 --> 10:50.191
you can.

10:50.483 --> 10:52.735
You see, but I'm...I'm not a Santa, I'm a writer.

10:52.777 --> 10:53.903
Ben, here'syour coffee.

10:53.944 --> 10:55.571
Christmas just isn't my thing.

10:55.613 --> 10:56.864
Your dad said you'd say that.

10:56.906 --> 10:58.199
How about for an old high school buddy?

10:58.199 --> 11:00.326
Except we weren't friends in high school.

11:00.368 --> 11:02.620
You were a freshmanand I was a senior.

11:02.662 --> 11:03.829
That's a no-go.

11:03.871 --> 11:04.955
Still.

11:04.997 --> 11:06.374
Once a Green River Hawk,always a Green River Hawk,

11:06.415 --> 11:07.375
right?

11:07.416 --> 11:08.584
Go Hawks!

11:08.626 --> 11:10.044
That's really more of a crow.

11:10.086 --> 11:12.505
I hope you find someone,I do, really.

11:12.546 --> 11:13.547
It just, it can't be me.

11:13.589 --> 11:14.382
Sorry.

11:14.423 --> 11:15.591
