11:16.676 --> 11:18.177
[Leslie]:How goes the Santa Search?

11:21.180 --> 11:23.599
Grace, if you can't findanyone comparable,

11:23.641 --> 11:25.142
I'm going to have to letthe network know.

11:25.184 --> 11:26.060
No!

11:26.102 --> 11:28.396
No, I actually found someone.

11:28.437 --> 11:29.397
You did?

11:29.397 --> 11:30.356
Mm-hmm.

11:30.398 --> 11:31.399
Who?

11:31.399 --> 11:32.692
Tom's son, Ben.

11:32.733 --> 11:33.818
-Who? What?-See?

11:33.859 --> 11:36.487
Oh! You must beso relieved.

11:36.529 --> 11:37.738
So relieved.

11:37.780 --> 11:38.864
Good job!

11:38.906 --> 11:39.824
Thank you.

11:39.865 --> 11:40.908
All right, we'llsee you later.

11:40.908 --> 11:42.368
-Okay.-Good job.

11:43.369 --> 11:44.537
Why did I do that?

11:44.578 --> 11:45.413
Why did I say that to her?

11:45.413 --> 11:46.580
Now what am Igoing to do?

11:48.749 --> 11:50.710
Tom! That'snot like you.

11:50.751 --> 11:52.044
Well, what'sshe going to do,

11:52.086 --> 11:54.380
drive to Bostonand drag Ben back?

11:56.841 --> 11:58.634
You know what,

11:58.676 --> 12:00.928
that is exactlywhat I'm going to do.

