Don't worry.

01:03:07.909 --> 01:03:08.910
Boop-boop!

01:03:08.951 --> 01:03:09.952
Oh, hey!

01:03:09.994 --> 01:03:10.912
Will the paradebe over

01:03:10.953 --> 01:03:12.205
before the gamestarts tomorrow?

